	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I thought it was pretty smart that Nintendo put a full wave bridge rectifier in the NES, so you can use any polarity and voltage from 9-14V (anything higher would start making the regulator hot!).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


